{"tid":2440916,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中大學生會前會長等人被控非法集結 警長稱遭蒙面男以鐵通施襲","createTime":"2021-03-10T09:51:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T11:29:51.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"38103158e5e84e6f88f80cb86087387056abc7fb","tid":2440916,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T09:51:52.000Z","msg":"民陣前年10月發起九龍遊行但遭警方禁止，示威者在旺角堵路示威，多人被捕，當中包括中大學生會前會長區倬僖。區與另外四名男子<span class=\"red\">否認非法集結與管有攻擊性武器等13罪</span>，案件今開審。聲稱遇襲的警長供稱，案發時遭一名穿黑色衫褲的蒙面男子以鐵通襲擊，但他看不到施襲者容貌。受襲後他一直追捕疑犯，直至在附近街市截獲失足跌倒的其中一名被告，該被告被捕時使用「頭套或保暖頸巾之類」蒙面，但看不清是甚麼顏色，只記得是深色，至於鐵棒則在逃跑途中丟掉。<br />\n<br />\n其餘四名被告均被控管有攻擊性武器或適合作非法用途的工具罪，涉及石頭、磚頭、鉗、黑膠紙及膠索帶等物<br />\n<br />\n控方要求播放案發片段，讓X辨認片中人是就是首被告。辯方反對，指片段影像不清晰，不能從中辨認容貌，而且X連施襲者的外觀及衣著都不清楚，遑論面容。此外，X或會利用施襲者手持的鐵通，以指證片中人是首被告。辯方指，裁判官葉啓亮的辨認能力不會低於X，完全可以自行觀看影片認人。"},{"pid":"c3841b08c10e9f52061a67c18ca1ea0d0ce59669","tid":2440916,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T09:51:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210310/DEY7ZCQ6JVENFO7WQXTVKCSTCQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210310%2FDEY7ZCQ6JVENFO7WQXTVKCSTCQ%2F&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplRT9vY2lxR77dvs0GIZdErU%3D&h=256dff19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210310%2FDEY7ZCQ6JVENFO7WQXTVKCSTCQ%2F&h=e02247b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210310/DEY7ZCQ6JVENFO7WQXTVKCSTCQ/</a>"},{"pid":"caf74a2038bf5d717960f2f7455feefcb05be6eb","tid":2440916,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T09:55:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8229c85a8e042250b2dd1fabcaa08c05f44203","tid":2440916,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03226d408690c9fbfca8f7602be38d0067d88ee","tid":2440916,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T11:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}